events.name: Open critique of #GE2015 graphics with Yin Shanyang
events.description: A post-mortem of #GE2015 graphics coverage with special guest, Yin Shanyang.  Yang runs the independent Singaporean data visualisation firm, Swarm.IS and we've asked him to throw his creative eye over Singapore's media #GE2015 coverage in graphics to cover what was done well, what was done poorly and what could have been done better. There are limited spaces for this event, so please register early. Where: SPH Auditorium
events.location: SPH Auditorium, 1000 Toa Payoh North, News Centre, Singapore 318994
